$ON_ZPFINUM1
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_ZPFINUM1 From W1SIPAR6
Return

$AV_ZPFINUM1
Call LECTEXTRA(zc,"PFOOTINV","DESAXX",num$([M]PFINUM1(indice)),"") From ATEXTRA
Gosub _AFF
Return

